cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with object detection and semantic segmentation of camera images. It may also belong to Robotics (cs.RO) as these tasks are important for automated vehicles. Machine Learning (cs.LG) is another likely category as the paper proposes a neural network architecture to solve both tasks simultaneously. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) are less likely categories as they are not directly related to the tasks at hand.
